rss.resources.app.Controllers

Interface AppContract


  • public interface AppContract

    ESTG - Escola Superior de Tecnologia e Gestão
    IPP - Instituto Politécnico do Porto
    LEI - Licenciatura em Engenharia Informática
    LSIRC - Licenciatura em Segurança Informática em Redes de Computadores
    PP - Paradigmas de Programação
    2018 / 2019

    Contract representing the App content structure. The App is used to store groups. Only one App instance should exist.

      • addGroup

        boolean addGroup(java.lang.String title,
                 java.lang.String description)
        Adds a group to the data structure used to store groups preserving the insertion order. Elements are stored consecutively.
        Parameters:
        title - The Title of a group to be added
        description - The description of a group to be added
        Returns:
        true if the group has been added, otherwise false
